Honestly wish me luck with this, because my...
body:
When I get home I’m going make a small video and do a meal prep for this week.

Honestly wish me luck with this, because my family decided that this weekend they needed to cook all of my favorite foods that I’m going to have to hold off on eating for the next year. 😭😭😭

But I’m mentally ready for this change.
